- Stop complaining. Hurry up and walk!

317
00:18:04,529 --> 00:18:07,069
It's only desolate for now.

318
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:08,489
Once we climb over this mountain,

319
00:18:08,489 --> 00:18:11,349
