382
00:21:43,539 --> 00:21:46,899
- Xiaoju—
- What are you doing just standing there? Let's go!

383
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,280
Come on!

384
00:22:06,940 --> 00:22:09,520
Taotao, look! Look at them.

