425
00:25:19,360 --> 00:25:20,840
If you don't believe me, I can show you.

426
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:23,529
- I beg you.
- Boss.
- Okay, fine. Stop, stop talking.

427
00:25:23,529 --> 00:25:25,039
- I beg you!
- I've had enough of you guys

428
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:26,429
