434
00:25:36,379 --> 00:25:38,320
It's one person's work.

435
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,229
Do a good job.

436
00:25:41,230 --> 00:25:42,399
Thank you, Boss!

437
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,230
You're welcome.

438
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:47,200
