460
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:32,109
No.

461
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:33,679
And it's by the sea.

462
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:35,480
So I'm really looking forward to it.

463
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:38,760
What's there to look forward to?

464
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:40,229
